Class GetAllElements

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.operation.impl.get.GetAllElements
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, GraphFilters, OperationView, Output<CloseableIterable<? extends Element>>, Operation

    public class GetAllElements
extends Object
implements Output<CloseableIterable<? extends Element>>, GraphFilters
    Extends GetAllElements, but fetches all elements from the graph that are compatible with the provided view. There are also various flags to filter out the elements returned.
